    "description": {
      "value": "<section class=\"secret\"><p>Any creature hostile to the [[lookup @name lowercase]] that starts its turn <strong>within 20 feet</strong> of the [[lookup @name lowercase]] must make a <strong>DC 21 Wisdom saving throw</strong>, unless the [[lookup @name lowercase]] is incapacitated. On a failed save, the creature is frightened until the start of its next turn. If a creature's saving throw is successful, the creature is immune to the [[lookup @name lowercase]]'s Fear Aura for the next 24 hours.</p></section><p>Any creature hostile to the [[lookup @name lowercase]] that starts its turn <strong>within 20 feet</strong> of the [[lookup @name lowercase]] must make a <strong>Wisdom</strong> saving throw.</p>",
